Package domain

package domain

Package:
domain

Description:
The domain package contains classes related to mathematical domains, including complex numbers and quadratic equations.

  • Complex - Represents complex numbers with real and imaginary parts.
  • QuadraticEquation - Represents quadratic equations with coefficients for the terms ax^2 + bx + c.
